item.title: Need Help With 317 Clients
item.dc:creator: @_Rich Rich
item.description:
@_Rich wrote:

What? If an item is ‘null’ it’s usually an item that isn’t supported on that client, such as you may be using Silabsoft item id’s on your client, when the id’s are actually much lower.

Although if it’s a ‘null’ and it’s a regular item just with no use, it’s basically a test item Jagex put in the game.
